pork and puha
Homonym Number:
Word Class:phrase
Sense Number:
Definition:perceived as a favourite food of Maori and used almost as a catchphrase, with variants, occas. jocular such as <i>Pakeha and puha</i>
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:puha
Pronunciation:
